{"sections":{"banner":{"type":"main-collection-banner","settings":{"display_wide":true,"image":"shopify://shop_images/One_piece_web_final.jpg","image_mobile":"shopify://shop_images/Womens_swimsuit_mobile_9.jpg"}},"image_with_text_overlay_8xYVyP":{"type":"image-with-text-overlay","disabled":true,"name":"Image with text overlay","settings":{"full_width":true,"image":"shopify://shop_images/white_one_piece_swimwear_The_Misool_Ocean_Soul_Bali.jpg","overlay":true,"background_attachment":"fixed","height":420,"mobile_height":600,"text_align":"center","caption_vertical":14,"caption_horizontal":100,"heading":"","subheading_text":"<h2>SWIMWEAR FOR WOMEN WHO WANT TO MOVE FREELY, LOOK AMAZING & PROTECT THE PLANET</h2><p></p>","button_text":"Button","link":"","heading_font_size":16,"subheading_font_size":16,"text_color":"#ffffff","button_text_color":"#ffffff","button_color":"#000000","section_space":"top_and_bottom"}},"custom_liquid_7pJLRF":{"type":"custom-liquid","settings":{"liquid":"<style>\n  /* Import Montserrat Font */\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400&display=swap');\n\n  .link-bar {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: flex-start;\n    align-items: center;\n    background-color: #f9f9f9;\n    padding: 10px 0;\n    border: 1px solid #ddd; /* Optional border */\n    overflow-x: auto; /* Enables horizontal scrolling */\n    white-space: nowrap; /* Prevents wrapping of text */\n    scrollbar-width: none; /* Hides scrollbar for Firefox */\n    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; /* Apply Montserrat Regular */\n  }\n\n  .link-bar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n    display: none; /* Hides scrollbar for Webkit browsers */\n  }\n\n  .link-bar a {\n    text-decoration: none;\n    color: #606060; /* Updated text color */\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 400; /* Regular weight */\n    padding: 10px 15px;\n    margin: 0 5px;\n    transition: color 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;\n    white-space: nowrap; /* Prevents text wrapping */\n    flex-shrink: 0; /* Ensures links don’t shrink */\n  }\n\n  .link-bar a:hover {\n    color: #fff;\n    background-color: #606060; /* Hover effect with consistent color scheme */\n    border-radius: 5px;\n  }\n\n  /* Desktop styles (optional, ensures links stay centered) */\n  @media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .link-bar {\n      justify-content: center;\n      overflow-x: visible; /* Removes horizontal scrolling on desktop */\n      margin-bottom: 0; /* No extra margin below on desktop */\n    }\n  }\n\n  /* Mobile-specific styles */\n  @media (max-width: 767px) {\n    .link-bar {\n      margin-bottom: 10px; /* Adds extra margin below for mobile screens */\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"link-bar\">\n  <a href=\"/collections/one-piece-swimsuit\">One Piece Swimsuit</a>\n  <a href=\"/collections/womens-bikinis\">Women's Bikinis</a>\n  <a href=\"/collections/surfing-swimsuits\">Surf Swimsuits</a>\n</div>","display_wide":true}},"rich_text_q4ed7V":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_block_YrcCYz":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"","title_heading":false,"accordion_enabled":false,"text":"<p>Ocean Soul Swimwear - where sustainability meets strength, and style meets purpose. Our women’s swimwear collection is made for water-loving women who need more from their suit: more support, more coverage, more confidence, and more performance.<br/><br/>Whether you're searching for a sculpting one piece swimsuit, a flattering black one piece swimsuit, or a surf-proof two piece swimwear set, this collection has you covered - literally. Crafted from premium recycled Italian fabric with UPF 50+ sun protection, each piece is built to last twice as long as conventional swimwear and is double-lined for support and security - no padding needed.</p>","page":"","center":true,"block_width":100,"accordion_icon_color":"#000000","accordion_icon_size":20}},"text_block_WB7pc4":{"type":"text_block","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"","title_heading":false,"accordion_enabled":false,"text":"<p>Looking for extra coverage? Explore our long sleeve bathers, sleek women’s rash guards, and high-performance rash vests for women, ideal for surfing, paddling, or sun protection. Need something warm yet stylish? Our eco-friendly women’s wetsuits made from limestone neoprene combine function and flattering design — perfect for spring sessions and shoulder-season swims.</p><p></p><p>Every piece of Ocean Soul swimwear is ethically made in Bali in small batches and designed to stay on in the surf, sculpt your shape, and feel like a second skin.</p><p></p><p>Whether you’re diving under waves, training in the pool, chasing your kids along the beach, or lounging between sets, our swimwear blends function, sustainability, and timeless elegance — without compromise.</p>","page":"","center":true,"block_width":100,"accordion_icon_color":"#000000","accordion_icon_size":20}},"text_block_j3dUHJ":{"type":"text_block","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"","title_heading":false,"accordion_enabled":false,"text":"<p>One piece or two, rash vest or wetsuit — this is women’s swimwear made to move with you.</p>","page":"","center":true,"block_width":100,"accordion_icon_color":"#000000","accordion_icon_size":20}}},"block_order":["text_block_YrcCYz","text_block_WB7pc4","text_block_j3dUHJ"],"settings":{"padding":30,"text_color":"#606060","background_color":"#ffffff","comman_data_id":""}},"slideshow_AfUbEA":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"image_iEkKgb":{"type":"image","settings":{"overlay":false,"text_align":"left","caption_horizontal":50,"caption_vertical":50,"hide_caption_background":false,"caption_below":false,"heading":"","subheading":"","link":"","button_text":"Button","second_link":"","second_button_text":"Button 2","slide_text_color":"#000000","cta_color":"#ffffff","cta_background":"#000000","caption_background":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","caption_background_opacity":20}}},"block_order":["image_iEkKgb"],"disabled":true,"name":"Slideshow","settings":{"display_wide":true,"no_autoplay